{"expireTime":9007200872922754000,"key":"transformer-remark-markdown-ast-17914a34eff6cdad4435f9dbcc456d14--","val":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"heading","depth":1,"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Web.play","position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":3,"offset":3},"end":{"line":2,"column":11,"offset":11},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":2,"column":1,"offset":1},"end":{"line":2,"column":11,"offset":11},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"strong","children":[{"type":"text","value":"visit: ","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":3,"offset":15},"end":{"line":4,"column":10,"offset":22},"indent":[]}},{"type":"link","title":null,"url":"https://zkirby.com/web_audio_visualizer/","children":[{"type":"text","value":"audio.play","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":11,"offset":23},"end":{"line":4,"column":21,"offset":33},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":10,"offset":22},"end":{"line":4,"column":64,"offset":76},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":13},"end":{"line":4,"column":66,"offset":78},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":13},"end":{"line":4,"column":66,"offset":78},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"image","title":null,"url":"../../writing/audio-home.png","alt":"Home Screen","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1,"offset":80},"end":{"line":6,"column":45,"offset":124},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1,"offset":80},"end":{"line":6,"column":45,"offset":124},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Web.play was inspired by FLStudio. At the time I was exploring the software and creating music through it as an (admittedly) short lived hobby. After coming to the stark realization that I was never going to be a great beat maker I put the FruityLoops aside - but I wasn't done exploring music. I started digging around the MDN docs looking for some sort of music related-project I could make with JS. I stumbled onto the WebAudio API and was immediately intrigued both with it's complexity and with the graph-like representation the docs detailed it in.","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1,"offset":126},"end":{"line":8,"column":555,"offset":680},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1,"offset":126},"end":{"line":8,"column":555,"offset":680},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"After a week or so digging around the documentation I was having a hard time visualizing the interactions between the various nodes and their roles. I liked the idea of building something that would bring tangibility to the audio nodes in a flowchart-esque representation and thus Web.play was born.","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1,"offset":682},"end":{"line":10,"column":300,"offset":981},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1,"offset":682},"end":{"line":10,"column":300,"offset":981},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"image","title":null,"url":"../../writing/audio-play.png","alt":"Home Screen","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":983},"end":{"line":12,"column":45,"offset":1027},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":983},"end":{"line":12,"column":45,"offset":1027},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"In essence, web.play is a graph-driven software for visualizing the WebAudio API. You interact with nodes as if they were legos - connecting them to each other such that some set of constraints is met that allows sound to travel from one end of the tree to the other.","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1,"offset":1029},"end":{"line":14,"column":268,"offset":1296},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1,"offset":1029},"end":{"line":14,"column":268,"offset":1296},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"My ambitions were originally to support every AudioNode but alas I decided to move on after I had reached a point where I was satisfied with what I had made.","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1,"offset":1298},"end":{"line":16,"column":158,"offset":1455},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1,"offset":1298},"end":{"line":16,"column":158,"offset":1455},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":17,"column":1,"offset":1456}}}}